3- Estimations: estimation_function.R
4- Predicted counterfactual outcomes: calculations.R
5- Calculations of MSE and bias: point_estimate_function.R
6- Estimation of confidence intervals: ci_function.R
7- Calculation of the coverage: coverage_function.R
